## 3. Commercial Use — Royalty Obligation

If You engage in Commercial Use, You must:

1. **Notify the Licensor** in writing before launching any commercial deployment (email address below).
2. **Pay a royalty of 5% (five percent) of Gross Revenue** generated from any product or service that uses or is derived from the Software. Royalties are calculated monthly and due within 30 days of the end of each calendar month.
3. **Maintain accurate records** of Gross Revenue attributable to the Software and make them available to the Licensor upon reasonable written request, no more than once per calendar year.
4. **Display attribution** in your product: *"Powered by SkillBridge technology"* or equivalent, in a reasonably visible location (e.g. footer, about page, or credits).

Failure to comply with this section constitutes a material breach of this License and immediately terminates all rights granted herein.

